    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for someone looking for a budget-friendly driver. While the car runs and drives, the exterior shows some visible wear including minor dents and paint fading in several spots. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant signs of age and use. Mechanically, it is sound for daily use, though it will likely require routine maintenance soon to address minor leaks and suspension wear. This is a solid choice for a commuter car or a first vehicle for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
