    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been a reliable companion for its previous owner. Mechanically, it is sound and performs well, with all major systems functioning as expected. The exterior retains a strong finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with normal driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-kept, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It has a consistent service history, making it a great choice for someone looking for a dependable, high-quality car without the premium price of a showroom-floor model.",
