    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a breathtaking example of automotive preservation, presented in flawless, showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, and has been kept under a climate-controlled cover. Inside, the interior is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple with no bolstering wear, the carpets are pristine, and the cabin still carries that distinctive factory aroma. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is peak-performance, backed by a complete, documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle.",
